{"tid":1497848,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大叔「食花生」變撐學生","createTime":"2019-08-23T07:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T07:24:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b159a21cd97f2a43b11b1d33c21803a263e0265","tid":1497848,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190823/20754477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F20754477&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1bCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=0839f9fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F20754477&h=2a3ba0de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190823/20754477</a><br />\n<br />\n大叔「食花生」變撐學生<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190823/large/1566493257_ea01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190823%2Flarge%2F1566493257_ea01.jpg&h=470c3062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃大叔認為香港出現今天局面，完全是林鄭一手搞出來。<br />\n<br />\n居於黃大仙數十年的55歲黃大叔，每日為照顧孫女、買餸煮飯忙得不可開交，對社會事一概少理；直至8.3黃大仙經歷全港首場「拖鞋革命」後，他坦言警方行動令街坊震怒，又形容警員亂放催淚彈如同放煙花，「好似唔使錢咁！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：深水埗母女：警察目無法紀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撐警街坊紛罵警<br />\n<br />\n黃大叔表示自己8.3晚有份圍觀，形容許多街坊都是「平常心去睇熱鬧」，更有部份街坊本來撐警，但目睹警員亂放催淚彈後都紛紛指罵。<br />\n<br />\n一連數日都有到場圍觀黃大仙警民衝突的黃大叔說：「第三晚落去睇，越來越黐線，一次射幾粒出來。」黃大叔指當時身邊街坊都沒有裝備如口罩等，「我第一次嚐到催淚彈，好澀眼同口渴，皮膚灼灼地，有少少痕」。目前他最擔憂催淚煙影響三歲孫女健康。<br />\n<br />\n自從黃大仙連日「食彈」後，黃大叔笑言自己由睇熱鬧變撐學生，「大學生將一生嘅前途都押落呢壇嘢，點解我哋唔多謝佢哋？點解唔肯支持佢？唔通我幾十歲同佢衝呀？我衝唔到吖嘛。」黃大叔又直指林鄭才是罪魁禍首，「點解嗰兩個字（撤回）係都唔肯講出來？你要公平，咪做獨立調查，後生（仔）唔啱就判，差人唔啱就審！」他又批評林鄭每次公開講話都火上加油，間接煽動示威者情緒，「好似當初啲人和平示威，到最尾林鄭話，要幾時通過法案，人哋咪去搞嘢囉」。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「亂拉居民 睇唔過眼」<br />\n<br />\n深水埗母女：警察目無法紀<br />\n廚師：瘋狂追捕太過份<br />\n「亂拉居民 睇唔過眼」<br />\n拖鞋革命街坊零裝備退暴警"},{"pid":"fabaf841059256f3474117ec6b6cd6a84af4f468","tid":1497848,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:03:02.000Z","msg":"切膚之痛先知是非"},{"pid":"0bd4118c873250c312ae2795b35195031af67a33","tid":1497848,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b37370960918679253c44878c7d8490c819926a","tid":1497848,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bd4118c873250c312ae2795b35195031af67a33","tid":1497848,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:19:39.000Z","msg":"而家先發覺有呢幅圖"},{"pid":"f32137dd3539b5c4fd2de80c06c542e4afe386c9","tid":1497848,"uid":75570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"親身體驗一次就知咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4d4bbd0d50f209824c72aa4545267c33d6a281","tid":1497848,"uid":165665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfed51c7ff4322350f2c72ac6891b393747f408e","tid":1497848,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}